name: Jessica Skaggs
text: I85  take exit 50 to cox rd to wire rd to Webster rd to pumphrey rd  to Teague ct you will NOT run into any low clearance it's a straight shot in Also very fast arrived docked unloaded all in 45mins

name: Brian Chapman
text:
Delivered here,  or tried to the day of the Auburn,  Georgia game.  I was a half mile away when the entrance was a low clearance railroad crossing.  There was low clearance for the next 6 miles which resulted in an 18 mile detour.
They close at 2 pm, and  I got there at 1:50, and ended up sitting on the load all weekend.
Oh well,  I  got a  restart. .......
Make sure that you have directions,  and  a  phone number for this location.
Also take Webster,  Pumphrey,  to Teague Ct.

name: Dennis McGeary
text: Fast and friendly. Even a little room to park if you’re out of hours.
